abstract: Saddling up for the Longines Global Champions Tour in New York.
snippet: Saddling up for the Longines Global Champions Tour in New York.
lead_paragraph: Fun fact about show jumping: While the sport may never shake its elitist reputation, it’s the rare Olympic event where men and women compete against one another. Also true: Admission to last weekend’s Longines Global Champions Tour, which was on Governors Island in New York City and showcased some of the world’s top-ranked jumpers, was free.

snippet: Mr. Booker’s presidential campaign rolled out a broad policy proposal that would offer a $300 monthly cash allowance to most families with young children.
lead_paragraph: Senator Cory Booker of New Jersey rolled out a broad set of policy proposals on Thursday that seek to significantly reduce child poverty, including by offering a $300 monthly cash allowance to most families with young children.

abstract: A look back at American politics from the year 2050.
snippet: A look back at American politics from the year 2050.
lead_paragraph: A crisis of legitimacy swept across American politics in the second decade of the 21st century. Many people had the general conviction that the old order was corrupt and incompetent. There was an inchoate desire for some radical transformation. This mood swept the Republican Party in 2016 as Donald Trump eviscerated the G.O.P. establishment and it swept through the Democratic Party in 2020.
